  Design Principle Applied

  "Every public method belongs in a protocol."

  When EventsService delegates 9 event-specific search methods through self.search, those 9 methods are now declared in EventSearchOperations. This means:

  1. Contract clarity - Anyone reading the protocol knows the full interface
  2. IDE support - Autocomplete works correctly for all methods
  3. Substitutability - Can create mock implementations for testing
  4. Refactoring safety - Changing method signatures fails at compile time

